OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FLargely dry and cloudy, but
OL,6,Falso some bright spells will occur,
OL,7,Fmainly in the afternoon before skies
OL,8,Fclear overnight. Winds remain light
OL,9,Fand variable.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FPredominantly dry on Tuesday, but with
OL,13,Fa chance of a little light rain
OL,14,FWednesday. Dry with sunny spells on
OL,15,FThursday. Temperatures generally
OL,16,Faverage or slightly above.
